    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "Made of the sturdy, thick hide of the aurochs and tempered to be both flexible and durable, this *+1 resilient hide armor* is imbued with the aurochs\u2019 natural defenses against venomous predators. You gain resistance 5 to poison damage.",
    "traits": [
